                  <span class="font-bold text-white">2 hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Actual first migration</span>
                  <span class="font-bold text-white">8 hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Actual second migration (with lessons)</span>
                  <span class="font-bold text-white">5.2 hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-2">
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Gap: advertised vs reality</span>
                  <span class="font-bold text-red-400">2.6x - 4x</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="wix-framer" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Migration: Wix to Framer AI</h2>

        <div class="my-10 p-6 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Medium |
            <strong>Time:</strong> 2-4 hours |
            <strong>Export:</strong> Partial (images/text)
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase mb-3">Steps:</p>
          <ol class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            {wixToFramer.map((step, i) => (
              <li><strong>{i + 1}.</strong> {step}</li>
            ))}
          </ol>

          <a href="/reviews/framer-ai" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#F5521A] font-black hover:underline mt-4">
            Learn More About Framer
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Migration: Squarespace to Framer AI</h2>

        <div class="my-10 p-6 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Medium |
            <strong>Time:</strong> 2-4 hours |
            <strong>Export:</strong> Partial (images/text)
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase mb-3">Steps:</p>
          <ol class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            {squarespaceToFramer.map((step, i) => (
              <li><strong>{i + 1}.</strong> {step}</li>
            ))}
          </ol>

          <a href="/reviews/framer-ai" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#F5521A] font-black hover:underline mt-4">
            Learn More About Framer
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Migration: WordPress to 10Web AI</h2>

        <div class="my-10 p-6 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Easy |
            <strong>Time:</strong> 5-10 minutes |
            <strong>Export:</strong> Full export possible
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase mb-3">Steps:</p>
          <ol class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            {wordpressTo10web.map((step, i) => (
              <li><strong>{i + 1}.</strong> {step}</li>
            ))}
          </ol>

          <a href="/reviews/10web-ai" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#F5521A] font-black hover:underline mt-4">
            Learn More About 10Web
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Migration: Any Builder to Durable AI</h2>

        <div class="my-10 p-6 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Easy |
            <strong>Time:</strong> 30 minutes |
            <strong>Export:</strong> Manual (copy/paste)
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase mb-3">Steps:</p>
          <ol class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            {anyToDurable.map((step, i) => (
              <li><strong>{i + 1}.</strong> {step}</li>
            ))}
          </ol>

          <a href="/reviews/durable-ai" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#F5521A] font-black hover:underline mt-4">
            Learn More About Durable
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Critical Warnings</h2>

        <div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-200">
          <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg">Domain Transfer vs DNS Update</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Transfer moves domain registrar (takes 5-7 days). DNS update is faster (minutes). Use DNS update for speed, transfer for long-term control.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-200">
          <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg">Email Disruption</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">If you have email through your old builder, set up Google Workspace BEFORE canceling. Email goes down if you cancel first.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-200">
          <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg">SEO Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Keep same URL structure when possible. Use 301 redirects if changing URLs. Expect temporary ranking dip during migration.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-6 p-6 bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-200">
          <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg">Downtime Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Plan migration during low-traffic periods. Have rollback plan ready. Test new site thoroughly before pointing domain.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- BRUTAL TRUTH -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-gray-900 border-[3px] border-[#6366F1] p-8 md:p-12 my-12">
